title: Plat Mid/Top LF Duo Jungler
body:
hey :)
i am a Mid and Top lane main and currently plat 3 after demotion (aiming for mid tier diamond) 
i am pretty lane dominant and really excell at snowballing so i am looking for someone who likes to gank early and has a good sense for making calls.

if you are interested just add me and maybe remind me of this article haha 
xXDelokXx  

have a great day!
